Package: robustcause
Type: Package
Title: Robust Causal Inference Core Bindings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dan Baissa [aut, cph], OpenAI Codex [cre]
Maintainer: OpenAI Codex <codex@example.com>
Description: R bindings for the RobustCause C++ core library.
    The package currently exposes robust linear regression with HC sandwich
    inference and Tukey bisquare S-estimation through a matrix-first API,
    with R-native formula helpers built on top of the compiled core.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    methods,
    Rcpp,
    stats
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
SystemRequirements: C++17
VignetteBuilder: knitr
